<item>
            <title>[LU-14917] allow switching mmap readahead logic</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14917</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We have seen some customer workloads doing mmap where the mmap readahead algorithm works very poorly.&#160; Investigation showed that the workload is much more like a traditional sequential workload.&#160; Changing the mmap readahead tunables and using madvise both did not result in good readahead behavior.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Instead, we tried allowing mmap readahead to use the standard readahead logic, rather than the mmap specific logic.&#160; This worked really well for this workload, so I&apos;m pushing a patch to make that a tunable.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
